My tablet is a little slow, blow is some steps to make it more fluent. My tablet actually perform better.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="version">
 Version
 &lt;a class="heading-link" href="#version">
 &lt;i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-hidden="true" title="Link to heading">&lt;/i>
 &lt;span class="sr-only">Link to heading&lt;/span>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Samsung s7 fe with 4+64G.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="enable-the-developer-options">
 Enable the developer options
 &lt;a class="heading-link" href="#enable-the-developer-options">
 &lt;i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-hidden="true" title="Link to heading">&lt;/i>
 &lt;span class="sr-only">Link to heading&lt;/span>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>In the Setting.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>tap the &lt;code>About tablet&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>tap &lt;code>Software information&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>tap &lt;code>Build number&lt;/code> for 5 times.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="setting-in-the-developer-options">
 Setting in the Developer options
 &lt;a class="heading-link" href="#setting-in-the-developer-options">
 &lt;i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-hidden="true" title="Link to heading">&lt;/i>
 &lt;span class="sr-only">Link to heading&lt;/span>
 &lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>under the &lt;code>Debugging&lt;/code>, enable &lt;code>Enable GPU debug layers&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>under the &lt;code>Hardware accelerated rendering&lt;/code>, enable &lt;code>Disable HW overlays&lt;/code>&lt;sup id="fnref:1">&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref">1&lt;/a>&lt;/sup>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>under the &lt;code>Apps&lt;/code>, enable
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>Suspend execution for cached apps&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>set the &lt;code>Background process limit&lt;/code> to &lt;code>At most 2 process&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="footnotes" role="doc-endnotes">
&lt;hr>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li id="fn:1">
&lt;p>: This options seem to be disabled automatically after reboot.&amp;#160;&lt;a href="#fnref:1" class="footnote-backref" role="doc-backlink">&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>